	   <tr><td colspan=2>My name is Naeaman, I am a level 50 Wiz.  If you follow the stream coming out of the dwarf city on velious, it leads to a cave with Wurms.  Some of these are green to me, some blue.  I was able to almost solo one.  Luckily my cleric friend showed up and helped me finish it off.  After that the two of us were able to kill quite a few of these wurms.  I started by using Bonds of Force and snaring the Wurm, then we just ping ponged it with damage spells...   <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
