<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=98321036439737></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f98321036439737><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=11&mid=98321036439737>RE: Where is the Velketor's Labyrimth</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=11&mid=98321036439737#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=3699><span id= >Alondin</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>11 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Mon, Feb 26th 12:59 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Velketor's Labyrinth is a dungeon in the SW<br>corner of the Great Divide, in Velious.<br>From the boat in Iceclad you cross the giant<br>bridge into Eastern Wastes, and then find the<br>valley into GD in the NW part of the zone.<br>You need a good group in their 40's to hunt at <br>the zone, and the difficulty goes up suddenly<br>and dramatically when you get deeper into the<br>dungeon, where a group of 58-60's can get into<br>serious trouble in a hurry.  Good Luck!<br>                           Alondin Octagorn<br>                           The Rathe<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
