<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=9778619422850></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f9778619422850><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=11&mid=9778619422850>1000pp - decent equip</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=11&mid=9778619422850#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Tue, Dec 26th 8:20 PM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I play a 45.8 wizard and I can remember his low level equipmentrelatively well I think. First, make sure you put all the points you could into INT.<br>For 1000pp buy:<br><br>Rings - (2) 2 int rings (made through jewlery) Cost: try to get 2 for 10pp<br><br>Earrings - (2) try to get 2 Golden Ear Studs (3int) from cubert quest in Qeynos... try to buy for around 40pp each<br><br>Head - Savants cap (has 3 int) try to get for 20pp<br><br>Face - Try to get a froglock skin mask (2 int-- about 40pp) or a bone chipped mask (3int-- about 80pp) Froglock skin is from a quest in innothule(not sure) and bonechipped is from ogres in WK.<br><br>neck - this is expensive so you might forget this slot and buy raw silk, however you can silver saphire (has 4int 4str) for 150pp if you shop around and are a good haggler. Next step up is sapphire platinum. (I still have that)<br><br>Chest- Go for your low end int robe- FBR (3int) GSD (3int but better stats)... I amnot aware of current price but try to get for about 125pp<br><br>Boot- nothing cheap that has int in this slot...buy raw silk<br><br>Bracer- There is woven grass bracer (3int) and PBB (also 3int) and if you find some try to get 2 for about 75-100pp<br><br>Gloves - buy raw silk (I have impskin but thats over 1000pp by itself)<br><br>Cloak - buy raw silk till you can quest for something better.<br><br>Legs - Raw silk buddy (I still don't have an int item here... if your budget increases a little buy silversilk leggings.)<br><br>Melee - buy a dragoon dirk (when I bought it was 20pp but it got rare.. try for 75pp) or a staff of writhing. ( I am guessing about 100pp )I think <br><br>Secondary Melee - Stein of moggok if you can get one cheap (150pp is a good deal)<br><br>range - this stays empty for awhile... you can stash that dragoon dirk here andeventually get a sacrifical dagger.<br><br>Ammo - I don't have anythig here... I used to see turmoil warts... and there are items with small stat increases you can find in kunark and/or velious<br><br>Total Cost: (going to count raw silk as 5pp and buy the more expensive armor items and both melee's)<br>about - 900pp, which leaves you 100pp to buy necessities.<br><br>       Slayyer Kamakazie - Wizard of the almost 46th lvl<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
