<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=97730426217982></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f97730426217982><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=11&mid=97730426217982>RE: lvl 16 hunt</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=11&mid=97730426217982#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Wed, Dec 20th 9:24 AM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Try oasis it's a good spot here was my strat. 16-20 do oasis. the DW caimans and crocs are okay if ya got a partner. A orcs are also a good source. when you hit 20th you now have 3 TP's tox is basically worthless, so just by NK and GFay. now you have two options. Unrest (if ya like choo choos) or lake rathe. Not I suggest lake rathe hunt aviak guards. Now there is actually a single spawn so you can solo em no prob. Personally I prefer the ones that spawn two because it's fun with a partner. At about 22 they become worthless so you should leave. Now head back into SK hunt gnolls and aviaks. Now if you're of evil nature you can hunt treants. If you do hunt treants it's a good idea to leave SK at about 24, because it's really crowded. This is hard to get a group for but the exp is as good as treants and good loot too. The druid circle in EK is a great place to hunt, but you need a big group. 6 casters is ideal, because basically the druids spawn like rabbits, so you'll be busy nukin', a chanter and one healer are preferred. If you didn't hunt treants than you should try mistmoore good exp there also, but again ya need a good group. at 29 the fun begins. you can go back to aviaks, to solo. Get a sow and clarity, bonds of force aviak harriers and avocets good exp. I'm lev 30 now and I'm huntin' in sola so hope I was some help to ya. oh yeah group TP's make a lot o money so get em early. but again the Tox one is useless.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
